    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/77a7dab45968289b707d6647331cbde8.poster.avif?t=1731402025\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/77a7dab45968289b707d6647331cbde8.webm?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/77a7dab45968289b707d6647331cbde8.mp4?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>🎲别犹豫，掷骰子！🎲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们邀请您进入Duck N Roll的世界，在这里，您将与可爱的小鸭魔法师和它的朋友们一起展开冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duck N Roll是一款简单而独特的游戏，您可以掷骰子并使用技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不同主题的关卡中，伴随着有趣、独特的角色一起冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/a5f0852401296efabfd30ffefb4a3d16.poster.avif?t=1731402025\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/a5f0852401296efabfd30ffefb4a3d16.webm?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/a5f0852401296efabfd30ffefb4a3d16.mp4?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掷骰子并组合点数以施展强大的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立您自己的卡组，战胜怪物！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/4faf315607a71f664ec2defd71217f66.poster.avif?t=1731402025\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/4faf315607a71f664ec2defd71217f66.webm?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/4faf315607a71f664ec2defd71217f66.mp4?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >各种强力升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着冒险的进展，通过组合各种骰子强化道具、饰品和纪念品来增强角色的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次都能体验到不同组合带来的独特冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/b11e2d308f692f907ad50eaf374cceb4.poster.avif?t=1731402025\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/b11e2d308f692f907ad50eaf374cceb4.webm?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3007390/extras/b11e2d308f692f907ad50eaf374cceb4.mp4?t=1731402025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单的操作和吸引人的图形</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简单的操作和规则让每个人都能享受乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，可爱的画面更是锦上添花！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小鸭魔法师和它的朋友们能否安全抵达目的地？现在就加入冒险吧！</p>",
